<title>Aw Bethlehem tang ka tun macheng</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1.Gam thiengtho a Lal hung pieng chu,
 Chunglam Aksi chun a zuon zela;
 Miching amah hawlte haw khanle,
 Aksi chu a en ui,
 Kei le zie aksi eng chu zuon zelin,
 Lal pienna mun tawm Bethlehem ei tunin.

[V2]
 Aw Bethlehem tang ka tun macheng,
 Chawl loin chieh ing ka;
 Sun aksi eng chun ei pui zel intin,
 Mari pawm lai Nausen chu va mutang ka.

[V3]
 2. Kumsawt Salem kawtkhak lopi,
 Ei haw din a hun hawng kit ta ie;
 Beimanna gama leng sa nung chu,
 Van khuo ei chansaka;
 Pakin la saitiu Lal thak a pieng tai,
 Lei hi kumsawt la hawih in thawng kimvel hen.

[V4]
 3. Lawplo a um dem Lal thak chu,
 Van mipite chun ahun khen tau;
 A ngaiin van khuo a thip zo tai,
 Kapin lei a thil ui,
 Kumsawt Aksi chun le a zuon zel a,
 A pienna Bethlehem tang a hun tun tai.

[V5]
 4. Aw tuhin ei le chieh hitiu,
 Mun thawmhau lam chu zuon zel hitiu;
 Lei lalte'n Amah do mahleu le,
 Mipihaw cheng inle;
 Kei chu ka Lal deih, ka lunglai nem pen !
 Mun thawmhauh um ale ei umpih ina.</lyrics>
</song>